subject: Cycling, Road
Bicycles and Bicycling
Vuelta a Espana (Bicycle Race)
lead_paragraph: Fabian Cancellara of Switzerland won the 11th stage of the Vuelta a España in a time trial, while Vincenzo Nibali of Italy took the overall leader’s jersey.
